he unwritten sex barrier that both parties have erected around that job."--cProvided by publisher.  aDescription based on information from the publisher.10aPeterson, Elly Maude,d1914-2008.20aRepublican Party (Mich.)xHistoryy20th century.20aRepublican Party (Mich.)vBiography.20aRepublican Party (U.S. : 1854- )xHistoryy20th century.20aRepublican Party (U.S. : 1854- )vBiography. 0aWomen politicianszMichiganvBiography. 0aPoliticianszMichiganvBiography. 0aWomen's rightszUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 0aConservatismzUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 0aMichiganxPolitics and governmenty1951- 0aUnited StatesxPolitics and governmenty1945-1989. 4aElectronic books.1 aJohnson, Haynes,d1931-2013.2 aMichigan Publishing (University of Michigan)epublisher.40zAccess to the Michigan Publishing online version:uhttps://doi.org/10.3998/mpub.5264551